12
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:32,700
[Episode 50]

13
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,100
Brother-in-law.

14
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,900
Brother-in-law, what happened?

15
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,700
Brother-in-law.

16
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,600
Hurry up.

17
00:01:59,700 --> 00:02:00,900
Hurry.

18
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:04,700
Run. I've been poisoned.

19
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,800
Hurry.

20
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,100
What happened to you?

21
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,600
We're being chased.

22
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,800
I can't use my internal force now.

23
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,000
Just leave me.

24
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:34,000
No, we leave together.

25
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,000
They won't harm me.

26
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,600
You should run now.

27
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:41,500
Brother-in-law, it's my fault.

28
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:45,900
I made a mistake. I poisoned you.

29
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:51,100
- What?
- The empress gave me a potion.

30
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:53,200
She lied to me and said that

31
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:55,200
if I made you drink it,

32
00:02:55,200 --> 00:03:00,400
you'd be in love with me forever and ever.

33
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:06,800
- Run.
- I poisoned you.

34
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,800
I will die with you.

35
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,200
Run now!

36
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:12,400
Don't move!

37
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,100
Let go of my brother-in-law!

38
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,600
Pardon us, Your Highness.

39
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:24,800
We were just following orders.

40
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:28,200
Release her. It's me you're after.

41
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:30,400
I will go with you.

42
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,000
Let her go.

43
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:34,600
Please.

44
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,400
Let's go.

45
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,200
Brother-in-law!

46
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:50,300
Brother-in-law, I'll find someone to save you.

47
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,800
Any wine?

48
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,200
Prepare wine for King Xiao!

49
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,700
Your Majesty.

50
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:41,600
Yes?

51
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,700
After a few days of imprisonment,

52
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:46,000
King Xiao remains as headstrong as ever.

53
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,000
I knew it.

54
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,800
This brother of mine is boisterous and obstinate.

55
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,400
Once he has made up his mind,

56
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:55,200
no one can persuade him otherwise.

57
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,600
Did he grow suspicious?

58
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:59,800
Not at all. King Xiao was just drinking in the cage.

59
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:02,100
Everything seems normal.

60
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:05,800
Keep him company and give him wine every day.

61
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:08,100
Don't let him grow suspicious.

62
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:09,600
Noted.

63
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,500
I hereby announce that

64
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:22,600
I will personally lead the army tomorrow at noon

65
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:26,500
to fulfill the dream of our ancestors.

66
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:30,200
The Song Dynasty shall fall.

67
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:34,200
Duly noted, Your Majesty.

68
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,700
His Majesty has been nothing but kind to you, King Xiao.

69
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:46,800
You shouldn't let him down anymore.

70
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:49,400
I hope you can change your mind

71
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,800
and help His Majesty to accomplish historical feats.

72
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,560
That's how you should repay his kindness.

73
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,000
Here, here.

74
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,000
His Majesty knows me very well.

75
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,800
I am not easily swayed.

76
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:03,400
Why is he so sentimental that

77
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:06,400
he sent you guys to persuade me?

78
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,700
I...

79
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:13,000
His Majesty still cares about the brotherhood you two share

80
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:19,500
and he still hopes that you can come back to him.

81
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:30,400
Brotherhood, you said?

82
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:40,500
Wine and food and some brainwashers here.

83
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:44,200
His Majesty is trying to buy more time, isn't he?

84
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:48,600
He incarcerated me but I'm still yet to receive my sentence.

85
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:54,900
I suppose he wants to conquer Song himself

86
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:58,000
and brandishes it in front of me.

87
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:02,800
He will tell me how even without my help,

88
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:08,000
he can still devour Song.

89
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:16,400
If His Majesty manages to conquer Song without much resistance,

90
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:20,400
he will release me and we'll meet at Bianliang.

91
00:07:26,900 --> 00:07:29,100
If he loses the war,

92
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:34,000
the first person he will want to kill will be me.

93
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:47,300
Let's go.

94
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,000
We have an assassin!

95
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,800
Assa...

96
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:44,800
As expected from the renowned Mr. Xiao.

97
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:48,300
One flick of the hand and everyone dies.

98
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:52,000
Fire!

99
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,600
The ones in there, listen carefully.

100
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,100
All eyes are on Xiao Feng.

101
00:08:58,100 --> 00:09:00,600
If he moves an inch, kill him straight away.

102
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,800
All right.

103
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,300
Hurry up. Lock the door.

104
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:04,400
Lock the door!

105
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,800
Hurry!

106
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:09,200
The emperor wanted me to ask you,

107
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:12,200
what you would do if someone

108
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:15,100
came to free you from a pinch?

109
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,400
In that case,

110
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:24,500
I, Xiao Feng, will replay his kindness with my life.

111
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,500
Really?

112
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:29,800
It's me, Brother-in-law. I'm A'Zi.

113
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:32,000
I told you I would come and save you.

114
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:35,200
No need to bring me alcohol next time.

115
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:41,000
Anyway, I will take your word for it.

116
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,800
Fine. Hurry up.

117
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:46,000
Open this cage and we'll leave together.

118
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,700
There are so many people outside.

119
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:50,400
Let's flee using another method.

120
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,600
Where's the key?

121
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:12,800
Stay in there.

122
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,200
A'Zi, what are you doing?

123
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,500
Brother-in-law, didn't we agree that

124
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:26,300
we would spend the rest of our life together?

125
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,700
Stop fooling around, A'Zi. Let's get out now.

126
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:37,700
Don't worry. I have a brilliant idea.

127
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,700
Don't move.

128
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,000
After them.

129
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:04,300
Hurry up. Over there.

130
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:14,800
- Brother!
- Third Brother.

131
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,000
Thank you for rescuing me.

132
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,400
- Are you injured?
- I'm fine.

133
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:25,100
Brother Qiao, you owe your life to A'Zi.

134
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:29,500
What? The Liao Emperor imprisoned my eldest brother?

135
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:36,000
He was poisoned and they caught him.

136
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,600
I managed to escape.

137
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:40,600
Brother, please save him.

138
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,600
Please save him. Send out the troops.

139
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:45,300
If you do, he'll be safe. Please.

140
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:47,000
A'Zi, calm down.

141
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,600
The Song-Liao relationship is fragile.

142
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,000
One wrong move and a chain reaction might occur.

143
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,500
If I send out the troops all of a sudden,

144
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:55,300
they might kill him straight away before I can rescue him.

145
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:58,500
What should we do? What should we do?

146
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:02,200
We need to devise a meticulous plan.

147
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,699
Not only did Sister A'Zi travel south to look for me,

148
00:12:05,699 --> 00:12:07,399
she also went to the Lingjiu Palace to look for Second Brother.

149
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:10,000
She even sought help from the elders of the Beggars' Sect.

150
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,100
Everyone came to save you.

151
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:15,500
I told you I would save you.

152
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,500
It's a Jurchen bullhorn.

153
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:25,300
Yes. Wanyan Aguda is here, too.

154
00:12:25,300 --> 00:12:27,800
You even asked Brother Aguda to come here?

155
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:31,000
They are fighting the Liao army by the East Gate now.

156
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,300
King Xiao, the enemies are abound here.

157
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:35,600
Let's leave first.

158
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,200
Let's go.

159
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,000
Big Brother!

160
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,200
Second Brother.

161
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:52,200
It's only right that I come to help you when you're in danger.

162
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,200
Thank you, Brother.

163
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,900
Chief Qiao!

164
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:01,700
Elder Wu. Chief Qiao.

165
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:05,200
As per the request of the entire Beggars' Sect,

166
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:08,600
I shall return the Dog-beating Stick to you, Chief Qiao.

167
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:11,200
Stand up, Elder Wu.

168
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:17,700
Chief, I appreciate your offer

169
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:20,400
but I cannot be the Chief of Beggars' Sect.

170
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:24,100
Chief, we were misled by dishonest men.

171
00:13:24,100 --> 00:13:28,000
We exiled you just because you aren't a Han.

172
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:31,200
We received a missive from the Dali Duan family several days ago

173
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:34,000
and we were told that you were incarcerated

174
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,200
because you tried to stop Liao from invading Song.

175
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:39,700
All Elders are moved by your moral integrity, Chief,

176
00:13:39,700 --> 00:13:42,000
so we used the Bamboo Trinket

177
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:46,300
and mobilized all fighters of the Central Plains to come to your rescue.

178
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:54,400
Everyone, you forgave my previous deeds

179
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:56,800
and traveled far to save me.

180
00:13:56,800 --> 00:14:00,100
I will never forget the generosity you showed today.

181
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:02,800
Chief, you're too humble.

182
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,900
What happened in the past was all due to misunderstandings.

183
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:10,900
You forsook your own safety for the millions of lives on the Central Plains.

184
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:13,400
We should be the ones thanking you, Chief Qiao.

185
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:17,000
- I agree!
- Thank you, Chief Qiao.

186
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:20,900
Thank you, Chief Qiao.

187
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:24,300
Brother Qiao, the recon soldier came and reported that

188
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:28,000
Yelv Hongji and his army are stationed 10 Chinese miles in front of Yanmen Pass.

189
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,500
Their invasion is imminent.

190
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:35,900
Oh no! Since His Majesty is leading the army, they will go all out.

191
00:14:35,900 --> 00:14:38,800
The Yanmen Pass is in danger.

192
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:41,600
I need to be there to stop them.

193
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:43,400
Heroes and warriors,

194
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:47,400
I thank you for your help.

195
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:49,000
I have to leave now.

196
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:51,400
Thanks again for rescuing me.

197
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:56,400
Big Brother, let me join you.

198
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:59,100
Big Brother, I want to join you too.

199
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:05,300
Together with Chief against the Liao!

200
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:11,400
All right then, let's go.

201
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:12,800
Go!

202
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:31,800
The Liao Emperor is leading the army.

203
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:33,500
They sure look imposing.

204
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,200
Yanmen Pass doesn't have a lot of guards.

205
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,800
How can they defend themselves?

206
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:38,800
The Liao deployed all of their elite soldiers.

207
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:41,600
It seems blood will be shed again.

208
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,100
No need to fear him.

209
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:46,600
If we all came, we didn't plan to go home alive!

210
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:50,000
We will give our all to fight

211
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:52,200
and show them what the Song people are made of.

212
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,200
Yes!

213
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:55,400
We learn martial arts to protect our family and our nation.

214
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,200
When else should we fight if not now?

215
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:58,700
Let's fight with all our might.

216
00:16:58,700 --> 00:16:59,900
Kill one and it will be an even trade.

217
00:16:59,900 --> 00:17:01,400
Kill two and it will be a victory.

218
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:04,000
Even if our blood will smear the desert and our body will lay here,

219
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,200
we fear nothing.

220
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:09,100
- To hell with them!
- To hell with them!

221
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:18,700
Heroes, settle down.

222
00:17:20,700 --> 00:17:21,800
Don't worry, Big Brother.

223
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:25,800
The 72 Islands and 36 Caves under the Lingjiu Palace are sending backup here.

224
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:27,600
They will arrive shortly.

225
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:38,300
My dear brothers.

226
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:42,300
Please help me contain our forces.

227
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:44,200
Don't let them fight recklessly.

228
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:46,800
Big Brother, what do you mean?

229
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:49,000
- Big Brother.
- Do not forget.

230
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:11,800
Great Prince of the South Palace?

231
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:14,800
Shouldn't he be locked up in the South Palace?

232
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:19,700
Why did Chief charge into the Liao camp alone?

233
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:21,800
- Let's help him!
- Elder Wu.

234
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:23,000
Be patient.

235
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:26,700
Without his order, we are to stay put.

236
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:31,000
Did he decide to surrender to them

237
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:33,200
upon seeing their immense military forces?

238
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:36,000
If Chief was a coward,

239
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:38,600
then he would never cross the Liao Emperor and be imprisoned.

240
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:40,400
If anyone says that again,

241
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:41,600
I'll fight you.

242
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:43,300
Silence!

243
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:23,679
- Your Majesty.
-  Did you come for revenge?

244
00:20:23,679 --> 00:20:25,700
No.

245
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:29,800
I know you have your reason to do what you did, Your Majesty.

246
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:32,239
The Khitan blood flows within me

247
00:20:32,239 --> 00:20:34,359
but the Song raised me.

248
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:39,179
You don't want me to witness the war between the Song and the Liao, and that's why you imprisoned me.

249
00:20:39,179 --> 00:20:42,059
In this case, why did you come here?

250
00:20:42,059 --> 00:20:45,180
I was lucky to have rescued you several times, Your Majesty.

251
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:49,199
You do not mind my lowly origin

252
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:51,240
and decided to call me your brother.

253
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,199
You granted me half of the land

254
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:55,580
and gave me a good job with a high salary.

255
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:57,999
Your intention was kind

256
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:01,080
but through my cozy life,

257
00:21:01,080 --> 00:21:03,880
I saw incessant conflicts.

258
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:12,900
The elderly lost their children.

259
00:21:12,900 --> 00:21:16,930
The wives lost their husbands.

260
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:21,140
The children lost their parents.

261
00:21:21,140 --> 00:21:23,360
It happened to the Liao...

262
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:26,880
and it also happened to the Song.

263
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:32,340
Once I conquer all nations, everyone in Liao

264
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:35,840
will live a peaceful and affluent life.

265
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:39,640
If you had been less of a warmonger,

266
00:21:40,780 --> 00:21:45,140
