282
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:03,620
What do you want?

283
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:09,500
On behalf of the Song and Liao citizens,

284
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:14,560
I want you to promise that...

285
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:17,660
as long as you're alive,

286
00:23:17,660 --> 00:23:22,520
