290
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:49,360
I am always full of myself.

291
00:23:49,360 --> 00:23:51,519
I call myself a hero.

292
00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:53,890
A hero...

293
00:23:54,460 --> 00:23:56,800
