294
00:23:56,800 --> 00:23:59,300
As long as I'm alive,

295
00:23:59,300 --> 00:24:04,180
I cannot watch you attack the Song empire.

296
00:24:06,780 --> 00:24:09,320
Can you stop putting me in a tough spot?

297
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:15,839
Expanding our territory is Liao's duty.

298
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:18,059
You have Liao's blood within you

299
00:24:18,059 --> 00:24:20,150
