300
00:24:20,150 --> 00:24:22,800
That's infidelity.

301
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:25,659
You threaten your brother, that's disrespect.

302
00:24:25,659 --> 00:24:28,420
You called yourself a hero.

303
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:31,720
Is that the hero's code for you?

304
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:43,260
My brother, you and I are brothers by name.

305
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:45,399
We live and die together.

306
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:49,540
You own half of what I own.

307
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:52,280
It's yours.

308
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:56,260
During that brotherhood ritual,

309
00:24:56,260 --> 00:24:58,720
we swore an oath.

310
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:02,320
Together, we share everything.

311
00:25:03,500 --> 00:25:07,640
Your life is mine.

312
00:25:10,620 --> 00:25:15,480
My life is yours, too.

313
00:25:27,180 --> 00:25:29,120
Brother.

314
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:32,260
Take care.

315
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,960
Big Brother.

316
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:15,919
I saved the Liao Emperor twice.

317
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:18,559
He and I call each other brothers.

318
00:26:18,560 --> 00:26:20,740
He gave me half of the land.

319
00:26:20,740 --> 00:26:22,999
He appointed me as the Great Prince of the South Palace.

320
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:27,980
Heroes and warriors, listen carefully.

321
00:26:31,560 --> 00:26:37,200
My brother, Yelv Hongji, gave me his words that

322
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:39,199
as long as he's alive,

323
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:44,380
he'd never send any soldier across the Song-Liao boundary.

324
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:48,720
I am a Khitan.

325
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:51,140
I am the Great Prince of the South Palace.

326
00:26:51,140 --> 00:26:53,840
However, I defy orders repeatedly.

327
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:58,580
That's disloyalty. I forgot my Han upbringing

328
00:26:58,580 --> 00:27:01,640
and chased after wealth and status in Liao,

329
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:04,100
that's infidelity.

330
00:27:04,100 --> 00:27:08,920
I killed my peers due to personal vendetta

331
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:11,320
and murdered my wife.

332
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:14,940
That's cruelty.

333
00:27:16,260 --> 00:27:20,870
I threatened my brother,

334
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:24,380
that's disrespect.

335
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:29,359
I am a sinner, disloyal, cruel, and disrespectful.

336
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:32,300
I have no right to be your brother anymore.

337
00:27:32,300 --> 00:27:36,159
From now on, you don't owe me anything.

338
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:40,200
May this reunion be our last.

339
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:43,399
I hope that you will think of the innocent

340
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,519
and stop waging wars.

341
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:49,240
No more bloodshed!

342
00:27:57,360 --> 00:27:59,359
Brother!

343
00:27:59,360 --> 00:28:03,000
- Big Brother!
- Big Brother!

344
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:24,440
Big Brother.

345
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:08,040
Retreat!

346
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:55,660
Big Brother.

347
00:29:57,880 --> 00:30:00,840
Big Brother.

348
00:30:08,280 --> 00:30:09,839
Brother-in-law!

349
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:13,400
Brother-in-law! Brother-in-law.

350
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:18,520
Are you okay?

351
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:21,920
Tell me you'll be fine.

352
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:25,340
You won't abandon me, right?

353
00:30:25,340 --> 00:30:29,040
You can't die here, Brother-in-law.

354
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:39,379
Brother-in-law, you promised Sister A'Zhu that you'd look after me.

355
00:30:39,379 --> 00:30:40,839
Did you forget about that?

356
00:30:40,839 --> 00:30:43,479
You don't want me anymore?

357
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:47,140
Open your eyes!

358
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:52,920
Brother-in-law...

359
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:57,240
Why...

360
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:15,020
A'Zi!

361
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,920
A'Zi!

362
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:24,260
Miss A'Zi.

363
00:31:24,260 --> 00:31:26,679
Miss A'Zi! Miss A'Zi.

364
00:31:26,679 --> 00:31:28,079
A'Zi.

365
00:31:28,080 --> 00:31:30,760
Isn't he the Chief of the Beggars' Sect, Zhuang Juxian?

366
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:32,880
What chief? He's a laughing stock.

367
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:35,959
A'Zi, I heard you came to rescue someone.

368
00:31:35,959 --> 00:31:38,320
I was worried about you so I came here straight away.

369
00:31:38,320 --> 00:31:41,479
How are you? Are you all right?

370
00:31:41,479 --> 00:31:45,259
Did anyone bully you? I'll kill that person now.

371
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:50,900
I am now with my brother-in-law.

372
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:52,639
I can never be happier.

373
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:55,920
He won't ask someone to bully me anymore.

374
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,940
Leave. Leave now!

375
00:31:58,940 --> 00:32:01,560
I don't want to see you anymore!

376
00:32:05,860 --> 00:32:08,980
You don't want to see me anymore?

377
00:32:08,980 --> 00:32:13,379
Yes. You gave me your eyes.

378
00:32:13,379 --> 00:32:17,340
My brother-in-law said I am indebted to you.

379
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:20,360
But I hate owing you anything.

380
00:32:26,220 --> 00:32:28,520
A'Zi.

381
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:37,519
- A'Zi.
- A'Zi!

382
00:32:37,519 --> 00:32:39,159
Don't do it.

383
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,360
A'Zi.

384
00:32:41,360 --> 00:32:44,000
Take back your eyes.

385
00:32:46,740 --> 00:32:49,620
We don't owe anyone anymore.

386
00:32:58,160 --> 00:33:01,919
- Big Brother!
- A'Zi!

387
00:33:09,300 --> 00:33:12,320
I used to pierce you with poisonous needles

388
00:33:12,320 --> 00:33:15,000
because I wanted to be forever with you.

389
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:18,200
Now, we're forever together.

390
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:47,760
Your Majesty, frequent wars over these ten years

391
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:49,859
have taken a heavy toll on our army.

392
00:33:49,859 --> 00:33:53,480
If we hadn't waged wars every year,

393
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:56,739
the Prince of Chu would have never been able to take advantage of our opening.

394
00:33:56,739 --> 00:34:01,880
The sacrifice of King Xiao was not for the Song Dynasty

395
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:06,520
but also for the Khitans.

396
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:16,820
Really?

397
00:34:24,740 --> 00:34:26,820
Bring me wine.

398
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:21,500
My brother, I will use this wine to commemorate you today.

399
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:24,879
A gentleman never takes his words back.

400
00:35:24,879 --> 00:35:30,040
I will never step foot in Song territory

401
00:35:30,040 --> 00:35:33,940
to help you fulfill your dying wish.

402
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:44,439
- Take care.
- Take care.

