411
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:14,400
Patrolling in civilian clothing?

412
00:36:15,520 --> 00:36:17,119
The Yan nation has just been rebuilt.

413
00:36:17,120 --> 00:36:19,979
We need to reorganize everything from the ground up and recuperate.

414
00:36:19,979 --> 00:36:23,320
No lavish spending, indeed!

415
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:39,410
